{"tid":1683150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日去太子拜祭嘅手足留一留意","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:36:53.000Z","uid":306569,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1b87071fcb3d7ea08386457602ccfaa31ef1e70c","tid":1683150,"uid":306569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"小弟略略做咗個簡單嘅分析 希望幫到大家 如有錯誤欠漏 歡迎指點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日太子站晏晝2時開始封站</span><br />\n拜祭嘅手足要小心 popo可能會進駐喺太子站入面 <span style=\"color: red;\">隨時由各出口伏擊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1j9dPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1j9dPW.png&h=e22ca2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">萬一有咩事 例如吖媽催你番屋企飲湯<br />\n走嘅時候 繞過各個出口<br />\n可經由大角咀等方向離開<br />\n時刻保持警覺</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後 希望大家勿忘初心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddc40743c9354222fe43c0023104fc47f5f0e43","tid":1683150,"uid":306569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫手推一推 幫到各位手足"},{"pid":"8c3bd1f3c017d1380a7e1e5c27183c68b0fb7370","tid":1683150,"uid":306569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"ece35b2faa89aa44fb5676b6e36a4560b32fb6e6","tid":1683150,"uid":306569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"ca8d887ff138b5b2e4e313d62e3d5fec484a5bfc","tid":1683150,"uid":306569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"